00:25:55,280 --> 00:25:56,900
Maybe we won't even need it very much altogether.

654
00:25:57,520 --> 00:26:01,040
But let's concentrate now on the gauge invariance.

655
00:26:01,940 --> 00:26:03,250
What kind of things can

656
00:26:03,250 --> 00:26:04,560
